sections.text:
Split: 515/111/111 train/validation/test (70/15/15%, random_state=42 ).
Features: character TF-IDF n n -grams (2–5, max_features =30,000, min_df =2, sublinear_tf =True).
Six systems:
(A) Char TF-IDF + OvR Logistic Regression;
(B) Char TF-IDF + Linear SVM;
(C) Char TF-IDF + Complement Naive Bayes;
(D) Char TF-IDF + Linear SVM + gender/age metadata;
(E) ParsBERT [ 16 ] , 5 epochs, early stopping;
(F) XLM-RoBERTa [ 10 ] , 5 epochs, early stopping.
All systems use per-label thresholds tuned on the validation set.
